&quot;Sure.  Didn't have anything else in mind for the night.&quot;<br>
<br>
He smiles again and lets his hand rest upon her hip, his arm around her waist as she drapes her arm over his shoulders.  He chuckles a bit and glances around for a moment.  Someone was there.. he could smell him before he saw him but that was always the case.<br>
