<br>
She stopped and inhaled the air with an appreciative pleasure. She gestured with a wide sweeping motion and a small smile to the whole of the surrounding area. &quot;Steve... Welcome to the <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>le district léger rouge</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bkalaberia.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kassen>Kassen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><i>~Kalaberia Citizen~</i></span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/15/03 12:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silhouettes in Vinyl</span><hr size=1> A slight frown creases his face, as he watches the two pass.<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em> Very well, </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> his thoughts boil darkly under a calm mask of contempt. Lifting his arms to the air, he quickly takes flight through the darkness, landing atop a nearby building. Hopping from building to building, he makes his way to one of the few spires that still stands in remarkably good condition. Hopping down onto a nearby ledge, he takes a seat next to a fiercesome gargoyl, and stares down into the street, forming a plan of action. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bkalaberia.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dhampirlordofmallorea>Dhampir Lord of Mallorea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><i>~Kalaberia Citizen~</i></span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/19/03 2:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=18>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silhouettes in Vinyl</span><hr size=1> George looked out the window of the building just across the street from the two vampires. He enjoyed watching the prey seeing if they lead him to a group that he could wipe out in a single blast. The male had almost caught his sent earlier, but probably didn't reckognize through lack of fear. Ah... Fear... Something for the weak to feel... just like pain.<br>
<br>
George reached into his pocket and fished out another ciggarette, even though the one in his mouth hadn't completely been smoked yet. He lit the new with the old and placed it in his mouth. The used one he threw out the broken window of the sky scraper. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bkalaberia.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dhampirlordofmallorea>Dhampir Lord of Mallorea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><i>~Kalaberia Citizen~</i></span><br>  Posts: 13<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/28/03 10:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=19>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silhouettes in Vinyl</span><hr size=1> The voice came from behind, where George was not expecting it. &quot;You know you shouldn't smoke, it's not healthy.&quot; Even though his gun was in his hand before the first syllable was complete, George still was unable to fire before the vamp knocked it from his grip. The three hits that followed, to the face, the stomach and the side, came with similar surprise and speed. The vamp gave George a chance to recover from these hits.<br>
<br>
Gasping for breathe, George decided to try to take the initiative and swung. Of course, being human and already hit three times worked against him. All it earned him was another hit to the face and a kick in the stomach.<br>
<br>
&quot;You really are stubborn aren't you?&quot; the vamp said, toying with him. &quot;It's a wonder no one has killed you before now.&quot;<br>
<br>
Hidden from the vamp's view, George was preparing a surprise of his own. When it was ready he stood up. &quot;That's because I do not play by any rules.&quot; With this, he took the bomb from behind him threw it and ran. Unfortunately, the only place to run was the window. Making a last minute decision, George jumped just as the bomb ex plodded. On the way to the street below, he grabbed a flagpole and the side of the building to slow his fall. He was still moving pretty fast when he hit the pavement and the force broke his left leg. George crawled to a manhole and lifted the cover with great difficulty. Falling into it, the sewer led him to a subway tunnel. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Well, I always heard they didn’t like it down here. Maybe now I’ll find out why.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#484848><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bkalaberia.showUserPublicProfile?gid=gwynnethdelioncourt>Gwynneth de Lioncourt</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://animatedgif.net/bulletsballs/flasharrowrt_e0.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle><i>~Kalaberia Citizen~</i></span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#8B4513>(6/29/03 5:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.jasminebecketgriffith.com/boredfairy.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Silhouettes in Vinyl</span><hr size=1> Iris led Steven into <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Ambroisie Sanglante</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, ignoring the red neon sign that loudly declared the establishment's name. This was one of the last havens the humans thought that they had, a place that was infested with vampires, and the cattle weren't even aware of it.<br>
<br>
The lights were dizzying, the music was pounding, and the smell of humans-warm blood and sweat mixed with a million perfumes- immediately assaulted her senses as she walked through the door into the flashing semi-darkness. <br>
<br>
She led Steven to the bar and told him in a voice drowned out by the music, but one he would surely hear, &quot;I'll be out on the floor. Have a drink and feel free to join me in a bit, if you wish.&quot;<br>
<br>
She left her jacket with the bartender, whom she apparently knew on a personal level, and headed out into the crushing and oppressive sea of bodies. As she swayed her way closer to the speakers, she thought mildly to herself. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Glad I'm not claustrophobic...&quot;</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showMessageRange?topicID=2.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showMessageRange?topicID=2.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showMessageRange?topicID=2.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showPrevMessage?topicID=2.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showNextMessage?topicID=2.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.emailToFriend?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.threadControl?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fkalaberiafrm45.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> C